{"tid":1825842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"達哥同我講「點都好要原諒子華」","createTime":"2020-01-15T15:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T16:31:17.000Z","uid":49336,"like":3,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"06aa1e803213eedc837bf37fc8d73014abf69c2f","tid":1825842,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:48:19.000Z","msg":"我同達哥相隔幾年冇出黎食飯<br />\n就約食燒肉放題聚下分享生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當達哥明白我上過連登幫佢平反<br />\n佢話點都好要原諒子華<br />\n一時間我都唔知達哥諗咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢就話人多食埋上太平山先再講<br />\n上到太平山達哥喊撚咗出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n達哥分享咗子華件事嘅隱情<br />\n<br />\n原來子華為兄弟...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YAKcQoV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYAKcQoV.gif&h=1ba8f3e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pwesEhg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpwesEhg.png&h=97fc1c4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p0GraoV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp0GraoV.gif&h=1d7905cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pCxxQoX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpCxxQoX.gif&h=e32c747c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XwyUjhj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwyUjhj.gif&h=3fe65b92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2SOAObz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2SOAObz.gif&h=b71178cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccGbmwD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccGbmwD.gif&h=2ea6b5bf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/oufjvuL.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoufjvuL.png&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=f85b1be7\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/oufjvuL.png</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/Op0GJQL.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOp0GJQL.png&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=bca8dd42\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/Op0GJQL.png</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/N3gFZrr.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN3gFZrr.png&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=2a4d09d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/N3gFZrr.png</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hrkCzQ0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhrkCzQ0.gif&h=4ea5c9b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TZ0-Y6loPRo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTZ0-Y6loPRo&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=61055e0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TZ0-Y6loPRo</a>"},{"pid":"3e67379e4cb2dd4655dc6c72ee48b9df347e3603","tid":1825842,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:49:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">GVG-907</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08frU5Z.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08frU5Z.gif&h=549c4a23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08frU5Z.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08frU5Z.gif&h=549c4a23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08frU5Z.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08frU5Z.gif&h=549c4a23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db476452cc258a51af894ad8ceb5e1383709a806","tid":1825842,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:51:42.000Z","msg":"GVG-907 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m0DX1MO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm0DX1MO.gif&h=a97b4a34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ae99e387501a12f84e89f23a40cf837efb2f63b","tid":1825842,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:52:47.000Z","msg":"放過子華了"},{"pid":"9e042cd2511d7a0592cf64594a1b07221b6a33e0","tid":1825842,"uid":45332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狗屎垃圾都放係時事台開Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉"},{"pid":"894998256baeaa612f20e16df482723a030dcf1f","tid":1825842,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10264e45497cc2b5286eacfad733599b49f0ac3b","tid":1825842,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e042cd2511d7a0592cf64594a1b07221b6a33e0","tid":1825842,"uid":45332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狗屎垃圾都放係時事台開Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:54:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6fed6860fe7a8b6dc4f5c032c103a2b04939585","tid":1825842,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:58:52.000Z","msg":"下面連登仔唔好屌我食飯<br />\n<br />\n我見其他人接納子華<br />\n我都接納埋達哥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家我兩個都接納的<br />\n<br />\n而達哥同我講接納子華嘅更強烈理據<br />\n我忍唔住同大家講<br />\n<br />\n下面勿分化同路人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbceec4c1cf982c13516b32f4f5d643ea593750f","tid":1825842,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:09:10.000Z","msg":"已原諒達哥同子華 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec4a0770bfa464cc3231269060d3555d9dd700f","tid":1825842,"uid":239525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:13:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac724cc1fe3535bd6e9b1d9ec50447dc8f1f7ab7","tid":1825842,"uid":139242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:22:53.000Z","msg":"咪屈 达犬出聲會無工開"},{"pid":"c379c242d69ee2bc50ea6d74340599dffa66fad3","tid":1825842,"uid":49336,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:26:49.000Z","msg":"六月，對達哥感到失望。<br />\n七月，對達哥感到憤怒。<br />\n八月，對達哥感到可惜。<br />\n九月，些少懷念每晚睇開台既日子。<br />\n十月，開始睇番達哥每晚既重播。<br />\n十一月，很想念他。<br />\n十二月，默默為達哥打氣。<br />\n一月了，後悔當初逼達哥關注。"},{"pid":"c8aacc59e9a0429df9fc2c0431a504e478d78729","tid":1825842,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:28:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不推文不推文不推文<br />\n不推文不推文不推文<br />\n不推文不推文不推文</span></strong>"},{"pid":"82d5b07aa7a7d6b2d6c4fe0385994b3d98cf30ca","tid":1825842,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:29:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不推文不推文不推文<br />\n不推文不推文不推文<br />\n不推文不推文不推文</span></strong>"},{"pid":"3e34c4200a8a106dea0c76cb6fb69e863ddc2add","tid":1825842,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82d5b07aa7a7d6b2d6c4fe0385994b3d98cf30ca","tid":1825842,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:29:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不推文不推文不推文<br />\n不推文不推文不推文<br />\n不推文不推文不推文</span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:29:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪撚不推啦 要吸引同路人呀</span></span>